# News Classification

News may belong to one or more categories depending on the content of the news. For example, News about a sports personality may belong to the sports category and entertainment category too. There are certain entities/keywords in the news which can help in determining the category, the news belongs to.

All the URLs that are visited on TIL network belong to one/many categories. Given the set of URLs (maybe as URLs or ids), their short/long descriptions, participants have to classify them across multiple categories.
